Liz Vassey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liz_Vassey 0 Elizabeth Vassey (born August 9, 1972) is an American actress. She is best known for her roles as Emily Ann Sago on All My Children, Captain Liberty in The Tick, Wendy Simms in CSI: Crime Scene Investigation and Nikki Beaumont in the web series Nikki Nora.
